\f0\fs24 \cf0 prism\
\
prism was originally created as a generative art experiment, exploring the subtleties of colour refraction of the surrounding colourscape. the triangular mesh is created using a technique known as delaunay triangulation. each point in the mesh is using a slight variation of the background colour to create subtle shades of its environment.\
\
the result produces crystal like forms with many colour variation and for this reason the app was extended for the iphone + ipad, so users could take part in this generative process to create their own favourite combinations.\
\
code by lukasz karluk (@julapy) :: http://julapy.com\
sound by by eli murrey (gentleforce) :: http://gentleforce.angrypixel.org/\
\
made with love using openFrameworks.\
