Horizons.\
\
Horizons is a interactive sound toy which brings together the atmospheric sounds of Eli Murry (Gentleforce) and generative visuals of Lukasz Karluk (@julapy).\
\
It is an exploration of colour, sound and form.\
The design of the piece focuses on creating subtle colour refractions in a rich colour scape using an algorithmic process known as triangulation. Fluidity of interaction is achieved using real-time physics made using the Box2d library. \
\
We hope you enjoy the experience and create a memorable composition.\
